            . The prisoner worked for me - here are several new files, which have never been used - men at times do jobs for themselves.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I had been in business with another man, but it did not answer, and we divided our tools- I sold them as I could, and lent some; they are common tools. <rs id="t18280221-268-verdict1424" type="verdictDescription">
